Test Name: Verify Preconditions
Subject: TC Now+ Vertical\WidgetRuntime\JIL\AudioPlayer
Description: Verify Preconditions
Description (Design steps):
1) Make sure all the preconditions listed are met. They will be required by upcoming tests.
2) Copy the content of the testsuite's zip-file's  folder 'audio' into the music directory on the phone. (The exact name of the destination folder may vary on your device.)
3) Click 'GO' to start testing.
Expected (Design steps): See green colored line on the device screen.

Test Name: play   Play MP3 file from device   virtual music test audio mp3 music mp3
Subject: TC Now+ Vertical\WidgetRuntime\JIL\AudioPlayer
Description: play - Play MP3 file from device '/virtual/music/test-audio/mp3/music.mp3'.
Description (Design steps):
1) Make sure you have copied the audio files in to the devices music folder.
2) Click 'GO'.
Expected (Design steps): Do you hear the audio play?

Subject: TC Now+ Vertical\WidgetRuntime\JIL\AudioPlayer

Description (Design steps):
1) Make sure you have copied the audio files in to the devices music folder.
2) Click 'GO'.
Expected (Design steps): Do you hear the audio play?
